creator: Thornton W. Burgess
description:
LibriVox recording of The Adventures of Unc' Billy Possum by Thornton W. Burgess.
Read in English by James K. White; Maggie Travers; Sandra Bennage
Another short story for children by the well-known conversationalist and writer, Thornton W. Burgess. This story revolves around Unc' Billy Possum and his adventures.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
